<title>USA: Micrografx Inc names Douglas Richard CEO.</title>
<headline>Micrografx Inc names Douglas Richard CEO.</headline>
<dateline>RICHARDSON, Texas 1997-02-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Micrografx Inc said Thursday Douglas Richard has been named chief executive officer and a member of the board of directors. He has been serving as interim president since December 5.</p>
<p>Richard founded Visual Software, which was acquired by Micrografx in April 1996.</p>
<p>Micrografx is a developer of business and consumer graphics software.</p>
